DEFINE
	VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
		TREATAS({"C"}, 'DPE'[Etiquette_DPE])

	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SELECTCOLUMNS(
			KEEPFILTERS(
				FILTER(
					KEEPFILTERS(
						SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
							'DPE'[Etiquette_DPE],
							'Localisation'[lat],
							'Localisation'[lon],
							__DS0FilterTable,
							"CountRowsDPE", COUNTROWS('DPE')
						)
					),
					OR(
						OR(
							NOT(ISBLANK('DPE'[Etiquette_DPE])),
							NOT(ISBLANK('Localisation'[lat]))

						NOT(ISBLANK('Localisation'[lon]))

		)

	VAR __DS0IntersectionCount = CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(__DS0Core))

	VAR __DS0BodyOverlappingPointsSample = 
		SAMPLECARTESIANPOINTSBYCOVER(3500, __DS0Core, 'Localisation'[lon], 'Localisation'[lat])

EVALUATE
	ROW(
	"DS0IntersectionCount", __DS0IntersectionCount
)

EVALUATE
	__DS0BodyOverlappingPointsSample

metrics.visualTitle: Emission GES totale en fonction de la consommation totale

metrics.QueryText:
DEFINE
	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'Logements'[Conso_5_usages_é_finale],
			"SumEmission_GES_5_usages_par_m_", CALCULATE(SUM('Energie'[Emission_GES_5_usages_par_m²])),
			"CountCoût_total_5_usages", CALCULATE(COUNTA('Logements'[Coût_total_5_usages]))
		)

	VAR __OverlappingPointsSampleLimitOperatorMinMax = 
		GROUPBY(
			__DS0Core,
			"MaxConso_5_usages_é_finale", MAXX(CURRENTGROUP(), 'Logements'[Conso_5_usages_é_finale]),
			"MinConso_5_usages_é_finale", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), 'Logements'[Conso_5_usages_é_finale])
		)

	VAR __G0Min = 
		SELECTCOLUMNS(
			KEEPFILTERS(__OverlappingPointsSampleLimitOperatorMinMax),
			"MinConso_5_usages_é_finale", [MinConso_5_usages_é_finale]
		)

	VAR __G0Max = 
		SELECTCOLUMNS(
			KEEPFILTERS(__OverlappingPointsSampleLimitOperatorMinMax),
			"MaxConso_5_usages_é_finale", [MaxConso_5_usages_é_finale]
		)

	VAR __G0CanApplyLog = AND(__G0Min > 0, __G0Max > 0)

	VAR __G0CanApplyNegativeLog = AND(__G0Min < 0, __G0Max < 0)

	VAR __DS0IntersectionCount = CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(__DS0Core))

	VAR __DS0BodyOverlappingPointsSample = 
		SAMPLECARTESIANPOINTSBYCOVER(
			3500,
			__DS0Core,
			IFERROR(
				IF(
					__G0CanApplyLog,
					Log10('Logements'[Conso_5_usages_é_finale]),
					IF(
						__G0CanApplyNegativeLog,
						-(Log10(-('Logements'[Conso_5_usages_é_finale]))),
						'Logements'[Conso_5_usages_é_finale]
					)
				),
				'Logements'[Conso_5_usages_é_finale]
			),
			[SumEmission_GES_5_usages_par_m_]
		)

EVALUATE
	ROW(
		"XTransformApplied", OR(__G0CanApplyLog, __G0CanApplyNegativeLog),
		"DS0IntersectionCount", __DS0IntersectionCount
	)

EVALUATE
	__DS0BodyOverlappingPointsSample

ORDER BY
	'Logements'[Conso_5_usages_é_finale]

metrics.visualTitle: Emission GES totale en fonction de la consommation totale

metrics.QueryText:
DEFINE
	VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
		TREATAS({"D"}, 'DPE'[Etiquette_DPE])

	VAR __DS0FilterTable2 = 
		FILTER(
			KEEPFILTERS(VALUES('Batiments'[Qualité_isolation_murs])),
			AND(
				'Batiments'[Qualité_isolation_murs] IN {"moyenne"},
				NOT('Batiments'[Qualité_isolation_murs] IN {BLANK()})
			)
		)

	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'Logements'[Conso_5_usages_é_finale],
			__DS0FilterTable,
			__DS0FilterTable2,
			"SumEmission_GES_5_usages_par_m_", CALCULATE(SUM('Energie'[Emission_GES_5_usages_par_m²])),
			"CountCoût_total_5_usages", CALCULATE(COUNTA('Logements'[Coût_total_5_usages]))
		)

	VAR __OverlappingPointsSampleLimitOperatorMinMax = 
		GROUPBY(
			__DS0Core,
			"MaxConso_5_usages_é_finale", MAXX(CURRENTGROUP(), 'Logements'[Conso_5_usages_é_finale]),
			"MinConso_5_usages_é_finale", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), 'Logements'[Conso_5_usages_é_finale])
		)

	VAR __G0Min = 
		SELECTCOLUMNS(
			KEEPFILTERS(__OverlappingPointsSampleLimitOperatorMinMax),
			"MinConso_5_usages_é_finale", [MinConso_5_usages_é_finale]
		)

	VAR __G0Max = 
		SELECTCOLUMNS(
			KEEPFILTERS(__OverlappingPointsSampleLimitOperatorMinMax),
			"MaxConso_5_usages_é_finale", [MaxConso_5_usages_é_finale]
		)

	VAR __G0CanApplyLog = AND(__G0Min > 0, __G0Max > 0)

	VAR __G0CanApplyNegativeLog = AND(__G0Min < 0, __G0Max < 0)

	VAR __DS0IntersectionCount = CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(__DS0Core))

	VAR __DS0BodyOverlappingPointsSample = 
		SAMPLECARTESIANPOINTSBYCOVER(
			3500,
			__DS0Core,
			IFERROR(
				IF(
					__G0CanApplyLog,
					Log10('Logements'[Conso_5_usages_é_finale]),
					IF(
						__G0CanApplyNegativeLog,
						-(Log10(-('Logements'[Conso_5_usages_é_finale]))),
						'Logements'[Conso_5_usages_é_finale]
					)
				),
				'Logements'[Conso_5_usages_é_finale]
			),
			[SumEmission_GES_5_usages_par_m_]
		)

EVALUATE
	ROW(
		"XTransformApplied", OR(__G0CanApplyLog, __G0CanApplyNegativeLog),
		"DS0IntersectionCount", __DS0IntersectionCount
	)

EVALUATE
	__DS0BodyOverlappingPointsSample

ORDER BY
	'Logements'[Conso_5_usages_é_finale]

EVALUATE
	ROW(
		"AverageEmission_GES_chauffage_dépensier", CALCULATE(AVERAGE('Energie'[Emission_GES_chauffage_dépensier]))
	)

EVALUATE
	ROW(
		"AverageEmission_GES_5_usages_par_m_", CALCULATE(AVERAGE('Energie'[Emission_GES_5_usages_par_m²]))
	)

EVALUATE
	ROW(
		"MaxEmission_GES_chauffage", CALCULATE(MAX('Logements'[Emission_GES_chauffage]))
	)

EVALUATE
	ROW(
		"MaxEmission_GES_refroidissement", CALCULATE(MAX('Logements'[Emission_GES_refroidissement]))
	)

	VAR __DS0Core =
